Photo by Rizwan Sayyed on January 02, 2021. Image may contain: text that says 'NETFLIX Home TV Shows Movies Recently Added You'll Love... My List Introduction Netflix utilises machine learning in a variety of different areas within their platform to enhance user experience and click-through rates. We will be looking at recommendation and auto-generation of thumbnails.'.

Photo by Rizwan Sayyed on January 02, 2021. Image may contain: text that says 'Number of upvotes Contextual Information Ranked Movies & TV Shows Seasonal Trends Recommender System Netflix uses a variety of proprietary ranking algorithms to recommend the most optimal content to their users to maximise view time and overall monthly subscriptions.'.

Photo by Rizwan Sayyed on January 02, 2021. Image may contain: text that says '3:15 NETFLIX Popular Higher ranked content appears more towards the left of each row You'll Love.. If the user does not click on the left most content that that is an indication of a disinterest. lome Downloads'.

Photo by Rizwan Sayyed on January 02, 2021. Image may contain: text that says 'Frame is chosen if fits certain criteria Meta Data of Frame: Frame 1 Brightness (0.4) No. of faces (2) Skin tones (0.5) Motion blur (0.1) Total frames in movie Personalised Thumbnails To further increase the probability of a user clicking on a recommended movie, Netflix incorporates personalised, auto- generated thumbnails depending on the user. So two users will see two different thumbnails on the same movie.'.

Photo by Rizwan Sayyed on January 02, 2021. Image may contain: ‎text that says '‎User A 3:15 l ה User B NETFLIX 3:15 Popular iI NETFLIX Popular You'll Love... You'll Love... User A has a different thumbnail even though the movie is the same Try it with a friend's account! Home‎'‎.

According to a new report from Reuters, Apple is aiming to begin production of their self-driving electric vehicle in 2024. Apple is working on a new battery design that would reduce the cost and increase the vehicle's range. Apple is also working with partners for components such as LiDAR sensors.
